{
  "stem": "7904.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But somehow he couldn't compete with-- with my father's business, because the Pollocks didn't believe him so much like they believed my father.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father was a very honest man, a very honest man, a good-- he bought merchandise for hundreds of thousands of zlotys, or dollars, just with a shake-- shake of his hands.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Till today, I believe in the same thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[CRYING] Well, my mother-- my mother stayed home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Her all-- her whole life-- their whole life was the family, the children, who had a beautiful mother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And her biggest pride-- her biggest pride were the children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one-- one sister was married.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "One sister was married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She had a boy. 1943, I think, the boychick must be eight years old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Also, the boy, the son didn't survive either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] I had-- I also had-- my oldest brother was also married.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He had also a young child, a boy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My second sister was also married.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Somehow it didn't work out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My third-- my sister, the youngest, but older than I, she married in 1941.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I remember that time it was the-- that time I was in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I remember, they send me a piece of cake from the wedding.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She didn't survive it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And my-- the sister that I'm-- what I'm most proud of, she was a highly educated young lady.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She finished like college, I would say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Her Polish was so well that she got-- she got from the Polish language, she had a 4.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That's means not a 5, but a 4.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "She didn't want to go and pick up the diploma.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She didn't want it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She had all passed, like excellent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "She didn't want it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And you will see her picture.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
